</h3><p class="sc-ZOtfp cLnRKw pf-79_ pf-text-1" data-pf-type="Paragraph3"><span style="color: rgb(74, 144, 226);"></span>Febrile convulsions in children and babies can be distressing, but with prompt and appropriate first aid, the situation can be managed effectively. By staying calm, protecting the child, and seeking medical advice when necessary, caregivers can ensure the safety and well-being of young ones experiencing febrile convulsions.



